Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:49.31,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}此刻從此開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:51.95,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}試著想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.71,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}自己能做到什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:59.49,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}有出乎意料的變故
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:04.61,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一定能夠越過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:06.74,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}power of dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.98,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一切從0開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:15.46,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}閃耀著飛向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.26,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}light blue wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:20.43,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}下定決心展翅飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:26.84,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}用最美的笑容  出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:31.92,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}現在向未知的世界起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:38.24,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}未來的選擇  做決定的是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.64,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}去追逐夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.20,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}也會有想哭的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:47.85,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}那是最重要的願望  不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:52.72,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一定能和明天的你再次相見
