Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:30.30,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}どこから朝になる？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.46,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}静かな空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:35.73,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}見ないふりをした指切り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:37.96,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}小指のさき
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.24,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}笑われた月なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:44.25,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}消えてゆくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:48.26,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}昨日の方角へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:51.27,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}嘘つき  臆病者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:54.28,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}みんなまとめてぼくなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:59.92,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}咲いていたのは夢の中だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:02.70,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}月の影に隠してた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:05.32,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}本当はね  泣いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:08.14,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}涙はもう流れない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:11.18,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}枯れてしまったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.94,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}なにもかも許せたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:17.60,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}流れるかもしれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:25.00,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}守りたいものばかりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:30.30,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}白晝從何而來？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.46,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}靜寂的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:35.73,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}裝作沒看見拉著鉤的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:37.96,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}小指的尖端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.24,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}嘲笑我的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:44.25,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}已經消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:48.26,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}邁向昨天的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:51.27,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}騙子  膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:54.28,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:59.92,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}只能在夢中綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:02.70,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}躲進月光的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:05.32,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我真的哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:08.14,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}但卻沒法流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:11.18,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}因為我的眼淚已經枯竭？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.94,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}如果能原諒一切的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:17.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}或許能再流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:25.00,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}因為都是我想要守護之物
